{"tid":1881623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被個扮手足嘅人呃咗錢，我可以做啲咩？","createTime":"2020-02-15T16:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T18:08:16.000Z","uid":130681,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ee1ca21c20f4f24f0b725f801d051db28481fc","tid":1881623,"uid":130681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:20:26.000Z","msg":"sorry我知我on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我玩app識咗個女仔都傾咗兩個月度，之後佢話自己係手足，有影過發夢嘅相比我睇，但唔知係唔係真係佢自己嚟。佢話同時屋企人又有事搞到手頭好緊，我見佢影晒啲證件同地址比我，而且上網又搵唔到有關同一個人嘅事就信咗佢。原本今日佢要還錢嘅，但我呢幾日都搵唔到佢，想問各位我可以做啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af66248e71522c0465183d2a2f208983a207d05","tid":1881623,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"呃咗幾多"},{"pid":"4e96e5c3ee9a753dc635cd1acce267e05eba9d65","tid":1881623,"uid":130681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2af66248e71522c0465183d2a2f208983a207d05","tid":1881623,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"呃咗幾多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:24:30.000Z","msg":"5500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f2263cc508f48b5c05282b375a88826da7ed41","tid":1881623,"uid":130681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:25:52.000Z","msg":"我應該等多幾日，定係快啲去小額錢債度排期？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3214ced034f4a122bcc5aad283d64613d6e9b8e7","tid":1881623,"uid":316715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"三唔識7都借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又一個衰咸濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243e5992e5dde6b35c0f33b61efc0dc786a8b76a","tid":1881623,"uid":206